    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/suneta-hostel-chiang-mai/hotel/chiang-mai-th.html",
    "name": "Suneta Hostel Chiang Mai",
    "detail": "I loved the Suneta hostel in Bangkok so I gravitated towards this one when looking for a place in Chiang Mai, and I was not disappointed. The hostel is modern and very clean - staff constantly are cleaning the areas. The staff are really friendly and helpful. The breakfast was absolutely delicious! One of the best for a hostel. The location is really great as it is close to the old city as well as the famous Sunday night walking street market. The bathrooms have a nice view of the temple nearby, with lots of light in the morning which I liked. The small single rooms are good value; my only complain is that very small bugs were crawling around in the room but that is hard to avoid in Thailand. I was so happy with my stay here that I have booked again.",
